.TH AFENDA 1 "2026-02-22" "0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
afenda \- afenda monorepo CLI — unified command interface

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B afenda
[\fIoptions\fR] \fIcommand\fR [\fIargs\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
afenda monorepo CLI — unified command interface.

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B afenda types
Type generation commands
.TP
.B afenda docs
Documentation commands
.TP
.B afenda guard
Guardrail checks (non-blocking)
.TP
.B afenda clean
Cleanup commands
.TP
.B afenda dev
Start development server(s)
.TP
.B afenda build
Build packages
.TP
.B afenda list
Show registered commands from registry
.TP
.B afenda doctor
Check environment (node, pnpm, turbo, git) and audit configuration
.TP
.B afenda completion
Generate shell completion script for bash, zsh, or fish
.TP
.B afenda man-pages
Generate man pages from Commander help
.TP
.B afenda readme
README generation and validation
.TP
.B afenda discover
Run discovery scanner manually
.TP
.B afenda bundle
Run all maintenance tasks (README, metadata, housekeeping)
.TP
.B afenda housekeeping
Run housekeeping checks
.TP
.B afenda meta
Capability Truth Ledger — scan, check, generate, fix
.TP
.B afenda project
Generate and validate PROJECT.md at monorepo root
.TP
.B afenda domain
Business domain package commands
.TP
.B afenda tools-docs
Generate tools directory documentation

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR -V,  --version
output the version number
.TP
.BR --register
Register discovered scripts into registry
.TP
.BR --register-dry-run
Preview register changes without applying
.TP
.BR --apply
Also update package.json scripts

